title: MP3s available soon
author: VD
content_html: I suspect that most of you did not get the chance to hear either of my two appearances on the Northern Alliance Radio show. I’ve just received both MP3s, courtesy of 1280 Patriot, and should have them available for everyone by the weekend, along with a few other things that have been requested in the past. Just in case anyone’s interested.
